Dependancies
============

- python-opencv = 2.0
- scikit-learn > 0.4.3 
- python-geohash = 0.1 


Display results in HTML5
========================
Open the following file with your browser 

slideotracker/player.html?mediafile=data/video.ogv&slidedir=data/slides&fps=25
